In ‌2023, Delta Air Lines became the first major U.S. carrier to offer free in-flight Wi-Fi in partnership with T-Mobile. headline: Delta Recognized as One of Taiwan's Top 5 Best Global Brands, Achieving Record High Brand Value with Superior 30% YoY Growth
